## **1\. users**

Stores authentication and role information for each registered user.

| Field | Description |
| :---- | :---- |
| id | INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO\_INCREMENT — unique identifier for each user. |
| email | VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL — user's email address. |
| password\_hash | VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL — securely hashed password. |
| role | ENUM('USER', 'ADMIN') DEFAULT 'USER' — defines access level. |

## **2\. applications**

Stores each job application created by users, including details and progress.

| Field | Description |
| :---- | :---- |
| id | INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO\_INCREMENT — unique identifier for each application. |
| user\_id | INT NOT NULL — foreign key referencing users(id). |
| company | VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL — name of the company. |
| title | VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL — job title applied for. |
| status | ENUM('DRAFT','APPLIED','INTERVIEW','REJECTED','OFFER') NOT NULL — current application status. |
| deadline\_at | DATETIME — application deadline. |
| interview\_at | DATETIME — scheduled interview date. |
| links | JSON — stores related URLs such as job post or OA link. |
| created\_at | DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT\_TIMESTAMP — record creation timestamp. |

## **3\. reminders**

Tracks reminders and notifications related to deadlines, interviews, and follow-ups.

| Field | Description |
| :---- | :---- |
| id | INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO\_INCREMENT — unique identifier for reminder. |
| application\_id | INT NOT NULL — foreign key referencing applications(id). |
| kind | ENUM('DEADLINE','INTERVIEW','FOLLOWUP') — type of reminder. |
| trigger\_at | DATETIME NOT NULL — time reminder should trigger. |
| sent\_at | DATETIME — time reminder was actually sent. |

## **4\. jobs**

Contains job listings and research data used for recommendations.

| Field | Description |
| :---- | :---- |
| id | INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO\_INCREMENT — unique identifier for each job. |
| title | VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL — job title. |
| company | VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL — company offering the job. |
| salary | VARCHAR(100) — salary information if available. |
| description | TEXT — job description and other details. |

## **5\. oauth\_tokens**

Stores OAuth tokens for integration with Google Calendar, Gmail, or other external APIs.

| Field | Description |
| :---- | :---- |
| id | INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO\_INCREMENT — unique identifier for each token record. |
| user\_id | INT NOT NULL — foreign key referencing users(id). |
| provider | VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL — name of the OAuth provider (e.g., Google). |
| access\_token | TEXT NOT NULL — encrypted access token. |
| refresh\_token | TEXT — token used to obtain new access tokens. |
| expires\_at | DATETIME NOT NULL — token expiration time. |

## **6\. email\_processing\_state**

Tracks the last processed email ID for each user to prevent duplicate processing of Gmail data.

| Field | Description |
| :---- | :---- |
| user\_id | INT PRIMARY KEY — foreign key referencing users(id). |
| last\_uid | BIGINT NOT NULL — last processed email UID from Gmail API.  |
